		<div id="comment_body_64211298">I really recommend checking out opnsense.  The original creator of m0n0wall, which pfsense was forked from, <a href="https://opnsense.org/m0n0wall/" title="opnsense.org">specifically recommends opnsense over pfsense</a> [opnsense.org].  The opnsense group is actually the one that took over the m0n0wall website from the original dev, <a href="https://docs.opnsense.org/relations/m0n0wall.html" title="opnsense.org">Manuel Kasper</a> [opnsense.org].
<br> <br>
pfsense also did some incredibly bizarre and shady stuff and ended up <a href="https://opnsense.org/opnsense-com/" title="opnsense.org">losing a lawsuit for it</a> [opnsense.org].</div>
