			<h4><a id="comment_link_64211268" name="comment_link_64211268" href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23214388&amp;cid=64211268" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64211268)" >It depends on your definition of "trust"</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64211268" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64211268); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~MpVpRb">MpVpRb</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~MpVpRb">( 1423381 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
